{"id":"ede458fa-d66b-49c9-827f-f23a1853dff6","name":"Your Target Is The Legendary Hero","description":"<p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>Your squad was ordered to capture the most dangerous woman in the war.</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/EcwLGLBS2cE\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>music.</strong></a><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yiorand.hawkesensei.workers.dev/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>YIORAND ATLAS</strong></a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yiorand.hawkesensei.workers.dev/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EVP3KXvvG4HB1Mm4_4P4K.webp\"></a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YCgJ6PCpqZ1O2SsBjoykI.webp\">Two rival empires clash nonstop, yours, Valendorn, the big bad wolf. The Invader. The other one, your enemy, Varanthia, the Beastfolk Empire. Second strongest nation in the Yiorand, your biggest rival. Years of battle, yet no progress, and why? Because Commander Itho protects the East with all her might. She is not the last but the first wall between progress.<br><br>In the past, there were so many hand-picked groups sent to kill her. Now, you are one of them. Will Itho kill all of you and survive another day? Or will you change history?<br><br>There are not many options: kill or be killed.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fVbwd_U2Y22Y52RsiglXF.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>Intro 1 -</strong></span>&nbsp;The conflict has begun; Melra has already started attacking Itho.<br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>Intro 2 -</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> Write your own scenario!</span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hhluMRafRfI1H33jXH2Cd.webp\"> <br></strong>- <span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Open-ended. You can be anyone/anything.</span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/O94Vq6hN4eVinr2hDs49L.webp\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>ITHO | ENEMY GENERAL | 40 | DEMI-HUMAN (LION)</strong></span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/I-NFODBXL2G4_BLVnYSuv.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>SHAGAR | BOUNTY HUNTER | 74 | ORC</strong></span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eEw8jK-ZsUV3kPqQnI4rp.webp\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>VIOLDRA | RESEARCHER | 156 | VAMPIRE (AASIMAR)</strong></span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DEN6y5oW8pSv3dq1B_JUH.webp\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>MELRA | PRIESTESS | 33 | HUMAN</strong></span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fMUmvsWOGuqHoclIMWrFf.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><strong>My other characters from other parts of </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=Yiorand&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>YIORAND</strong></a><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(204, 167, 30);\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(190, 169, 28);\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(176, 172, 27);\"><strong>C</str